snippet.title: 26 Rob Plays Trailer
snippet.description:
26 Rob Plays is a pass and play style VR game where you complete against other players across a range of mini-games. Challenge up to 8 friends or family members in this local co-op shared VR experience. 

Backseat drivers have nothing on backseat burger assemblers, cannon dodgers and icecream engineers.

26 Rob Plays is fun and fast paced as you and your opponents swap in and out of games.

Enjoy dozens of fun games that make the most of VR interactivity and beat your opponents to earn Rob's Personal Seal of A Well Spent Saturday Night (yep that's a thing).
